node.text: Are you a complete beginner to the stock market, and have no idea where to begin? Then click the link in my bio to grab my beginners guide! Feel free to send me a DM if you have any questions! :)

Human nature. Investing in general is a huge one.

We are all guilty of this to some degree. It’s always a good idea to work on deeply understanding what something actually is before just quickly dismissing it. Do research to try and find the fundamental truth before dismissing something. 💯🔥
Here are some expected 2021 IPOs. Are you watching any of them? 🤔
Master these and you’ll master money

As cliche as it sounds, mindset really IS everything. 💯🔥

You’ll never become rich if you don’t believe it’s possible

“I always knew I was going to be rich. I don't think I ever doubted it for a minute.” - Warren Buffett

Marriage is a partnership. WHO you pick to be your partner is one of the most important decisions in life, especially when it comes to your financial future.

Most marriage problems occur due to money issues. If you aren’t on the same page financially when it comes to your loved ones, conflict is bound to happen. 
-
